DataList.LocalizeJP: 了解っす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Understood!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私っすか？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Me?

DataList.LocalizeJP: あれ？出番、間違えたっすか？
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's my turn, right? Did I get it wrong?

DataList.LocalizeJP: ふん……
なるほど、こういう感じだったんすねぇ……。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I see. So, it's like this...

DataList.LocalizeJP: いよいよ始まるっすね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's finally starting, huh?

DataList.LocalizeJP: いやー、やることが一杯っす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Phew! There sure is a lot to do.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 皆さん、お疲れ様っす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Good work, everyone!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ふぅ、一段落ついたし、帰るっすよ～！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Phew. Things calmed down for now. I'm heading back!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 助かったっす！
DataList.LocalizeEN: That helped!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 本気で行くっすよ。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm getting serious.

DataList.LocalizeJP: おっと。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Whoa.

DataList.LocalizeJP: おお！
あれ…
あはは…
無駄っすよ～
DataList.LocalizeEN: You can't hit me.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 私についてこーい！これでいいっすか？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Everyone follow me!... Did that sound good?

DataList.LocalizeJP: さぁ、いくっすよ～！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Alright, here I go!

DataList.LocalizeJP: さっさと終わらせるっす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Let's get this over quick.

DataList.LocalizeJP: この調子で行くっすよ～。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Keep going at that pace.

DataList.LocalizeJP: やっほ～！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Yoo-hoo!

DataList.LocalizeJP: ちっ……
DataList.LocalizeEN: Tsk...

DataList.LocalizeJP: やっ！
ふーん…
よいしょっと！
皆さん、本当凄いっすね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: You all are truly amazing.

DataList.LocalizeJP: いやー、何とかなるもんっすね～。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Phew! Things just work out sometimes.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 上手くいったんすかね？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Did that really work?

DataList.LocalizeJP: あーあ、またっすか？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Haaa, again?

DataList.LocalizeJP: はっ、もう勘弁してほしいっす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Sigh, give me a break.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今取り込み中っす。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'm in the middle of something right now.

DataList.LocalizeJP: じゃ、頼んだっすよ！
DataList.LocalizeEN: Alright, I leave it to you!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 今度奢るんで！
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll treat you to something next time!

DataList.LocalizeJP: 後でいいっすか？今取り込み中で。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Can we do this later? I'm in the middle of something right now.

DataList.LocalizeJP: あっ、くれるんすか？ありがとーっす、先生。
DataList.LocalizeEN: What?... For me? Thank you so much, Sensei.

DataList.LocalizeJP: そんなことしても、別に何も出ないっすよ？
DataList.LocalizeEN: Giving me this won't get you anything, you know, right?

DataList.LocalizeJP: あははっ、こんだけ貰っちゃったら、メチャクチャ頑張るしかないっすね。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Ahaha, when you give me so much, I have no choice but to give it my absolute all.

DataList.LocalizeJP: えーと、光栄っすけど……その、えへへ……。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Umm, I'm honored, you know, it's just... Ehehe...

DataList.LocalizeJP: その、困りました……何とお礼を言えば……。
DataList.LocalizeEN: Umm, this is tough... How should I thank you...

DataList.LocalizeJP: こういう時って、素直に喜んでいいんです……よね？
DataList.LocalizeEN: In a situation like this, I guess I should just be sincere, right?

DataList.LocalizeJP: このご恩はいつか必ず返すっす。どういう風に返すかは、その時までのお楽しみ、ってことで。
DataList.LocalizeEN: I'll make up for this one day. But what will I do in return? I guess that's one thing to look forward to.

DataList.LocalizeJP: 何だか、こそばゆいというか、妙な感じがするっす。気のせい、っすかね？
DataList.LocalizeEN: It's a bit embarrasing, don't you think? Is it just me?
